arguments.desc:
If set to -1, we use global mean;
if set to  > 0 and <1, it used as a quantile value to find the cutoff value; 
If set to any number that is greater or equal to 1, the absolute cutoff is applied to remove miRNA species.

The miRNA species will be removed only when ALL samples failed to meet the criteria: the read counts are greater or equal to the cutoff.

